snippet.title: Playtonic Friends Presents: BPM: Bullets Per Minute is OUT NOW
snippet.description:
BPM is OUT NOW on PS4 and Xbox One!!

PlayStation: https://bit.ly/BPMPS4
Xbox: https://bit.ly/BPMxbox

Also playable on PS5 and Xbox Series X|S (runs up to 4k 60fps!).

Love the soundtrack? You can buy it here: https://bit.ly/2SrSdjy

Follow Playtonic Friends and Awe Interactive on Twitter to be kept up-to-date with more news: 
Playtonic Friends: https://twitter.com/PTonicFriends​​ 
BPM: https://twitter.com/bpmgame
Awe Interactive: https://twitter.com/AweInteractive
